{"tid":2311932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[支那style] 北京小男孩地鐵上大罵奶奶逼讓座 網民憤慨","createTime":"2020-12-04T12:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T03:45:03.000Z","uid":251732,"like":197,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"b28e2b33c4fd9602beaa543df516cb72a8bcb058","tid":2311932,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:28:49.000Z","msg":"近日，北京一名男童在地鐵上大聲辱罵自己的奶奶，逼奶奶讓座給他，並且對著奶奶各種咆哮。此舉引發大陸網民的憤慨，批評男童目無尊長，欠管教。<br />\n<br />\n有北京網友把12月2日發生在地鐵4號線上的這段視頻放在網上，引關注。當天，奶奶接孫子下課，這名男童在地鐵上要奶奶讓座。<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><br />\n根據視頻顯示，這名男孩手指著奶奶大吼：「我警告你，你給我起來，起來！你是個什麼東西！聽不懂人話嗎？」奶奶對著他說：「你要是再大聲喧嘩，一會兒下了地鐵我就自己走了，因為你這種孩子不能要！」</span><br />\n<br />\n據陸媒報導，後來有了空座，奶奶讓他坐，他不坐，奶奶自己坐下後，小男孩卻要求自己奶奶站起來，還大聲說：「就不讓你這個老東西坐」，還對著奶奶大吼大叫：「起來你，你起來&hellip;&hellip;我再說一遍，你起來&hellip;&hellip;。」<br />\n<br />\n旁邊的一位女乘客看不下去了，就說：「你做的事讓大家都看不慣，你知道嗎？你這樣做不對。」就問小男孩：「小朋友你哪個學校的？」<br />\n<br />\n小男孩對著女子喊道：「臭學校，別管我。幹你的事去，別管我」。<br />\n<br />\n報導說，奶奶看到大家在拍視頻，並沒有阻止，看得出她很無奈，奶奶指著他說：這要不管，早晚成流氓，社會渣滓。<br />\n<br />\n小男孩說出極其難聽的話、目無尊長的行為，引起大陸網民的一陣批評。<br />\n<br />\n「這樣的孩子長大對社會危害太大。」「這是父母的錯，教育有問題」「這都是家裡大人慣的，再不管就真的廢了。」「父母可能平時就是這樣對待奶奶的。」「子不教父之過啊！養兒不教，等於白養！」「這個社會生病了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i4.ponews.net/4a243e724c454986ae019371cd7cf803230790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi4.ponews.net%2F4a243e724c454986ae019371cd7cf803230790.jpg&h=21a4c0c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/12/4/n12595640.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F12%2F4%2Fn12595640.htm&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=ca6bf777\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/12/4/n12595640.htm</a><br />\n責任編輯：許夢兒"},{"pid":"e65010699ee406788313e2e38319c5e38b1dc6dc","tid":2311932,"uid":70487,"like":102,"dislike":2,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"男童辱大奶奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d28b311752f8897324b3b41530bc60a548d5cc2","tid":2311932,"uid":318300,"like":91,"dislike":3,"score":88,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"符合國情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad0a3d67d664761a32f0db14da0bd3bb3673ade","tid":2311932,"uid":251732,"like":200,"dislike":3,"score":197,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T88TWeZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT88TWeZ.gif&h=0c2917dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39115469b4262ad56b1deaad4d0dda98d6187316","tid":2311932,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"07be4454f967546ba468f63144c4125912f06561","tid":2311932,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"6b1d15fe2a2983bc77d1d0234b02779526e7f05e","tid":2311932,"uid":34714,"like":119,"dislike":3,"score":116,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"男孩竟然有這麼大的奶奶"},{"pid":"386ca1c341e8e9b647fa5afb69d5c1d1589fb2c2","tid":2311932,"uid":49336,"like":25,"dislike":11,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:32:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f326797548faab1e27eabb61969bb458821c1a0b","tid":2311932,"uid":251732,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:32:43.000Z","msg":"push 3"},{"pid":"a632bd195f4fc2afc3a5b33c7531ebe50a44c8eb","tid":2311932,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"cite